I remember the day I ended up in the shelter back in May 2015. My people had not been home for a few days and I was super hungry, thirsty and lonely.
I would watch out the porch windows waiting for them to come back. Suddenly I saw two humans approach my house. I was so happy to see a human it had been days since I had seen one. They came to the door and could tell I had been alone for a while since I was skinny and the porch I was in was a mess since I could not get outside. They took me to the shelter. I was very grateful for the warm bed, food and water but still wondered when my people would return......They never did!
I have now been in the shelter for three years. I love all my shelter moms and friends but really want a home of my own!!!
PLEASE HELP ME !!!!
XOXO, COCO

Contact Goodmewsrescue@gmail.com to meet this adorable baby.
